title.narrative: Advocacy and Communication

description.narrative: The updated office advocacy communication strategy and a COVID-19 advocacy sub-strategy, together with the extension of online platforms, improved public outreach on children’s rights and COVID-19 prevention. In 2021, UNICEF social media followers increased by 30 per cent on Instagram, 20 per cent on Facebook, 30 per cent on Twitter. UNICEF produced 44 events, 100 video including some done with celebrities and adolescents, 14 stories, 4 op-eds, 22 national and 60 localized global press releases, and 20 speeches, contributing to 500 mentions of UNICEF in national print media and posts seen 500 million times online, including 10 million video views.; | Status:On-track | As-of Date:29/12/2021
